      <TextArea editable="false" layoutX="14.0" layoutY="545.0" prefHeight="291.0" prefWidth="911.0" text="Transmission of Coronavirus to humans may occur when one comes in direct contact with infected people or animals. The recent &#10;outbreak of Coronavirus in China occurred when an old man bought infected seafood. Coronavirus is also transmitted through &#10;coughing, sneezing. This infection can also easily affect people who come in direct contact with contaminated bodies. &#10;&#10;The symptoms of this virus are:&#10;1)  Runny Nose            &#10;2) Cough                        &#10;3) Sore Throat&#10;4) Fever&#10;5) Pneumonia     &#10;6) Cardiovascular Symptoms&#10;7) Shortness of Breath&#10;8) Kidney Failure&#10;">
